# Normalize text files automatically.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Source files
*.ts text
*.tsx text
*.js text
*.jsx text
*.json text
*.css text
*.scss text
*.html text
*.md text
*.yml text
*.yaml text

# Images
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.svg text

# Fonts
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary